# Pull and Override Code

Override the local `sprint-relay` code with the specified branch from `https://github.com/pdtoan2811-bit/sprintDebugStaging`.

## User Review Required

> [!WARNING]
> This will perform a `git reset --hard`, which will **permanently delete** any uncommitted local changes and any commits that are not present in the remote repository.

## Proposed Changes

### [Git Operations]

#### [ACTION] [Update Git Remote]
- Add the new remote URL: `https://github.com/pdtoan2811-bit/sprintDebugStaging` (as `staging` or update `origin`).
- Fetch the latest changes from the remote.
- Perform a `git reset --hard` to the remote's main branch (e.g., `staging/main` or `staging/master`).

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `git status` after the reset to confirm the state.
- Run `git log -1` to verify the latest commit matches the remote.
- Run `npm run dev` (if applicable) to ensure the application starts correctly.
